description:
Detective, are you ready to take the case? Find out what happened to the young aristocrat, investigate the haunted mansion and uncover the truth behind the Old Painting's Ghost in this chilling hidden object game. Don't expect it to be easy. With special paints and brushes, you'll even have to enter the paintings around the grand estate and hunt for clues inside the artwork. Become a part of the story and the paintings in Old Painting's Ghost today!
